"{\"uid\": \"cyclingnews.com-races-olympic-games-2024-track-cycling-women-s-omnium-results\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"  US rider dominates across the day of racing as Poland and New Zealand take silver and bronze  When you purchase through links on our site, we may earn an affiliate commission.Here's how it works.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 197, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 49, \"end\": 55, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Poland_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9969016706212502, \"rank\": 0.002971336519427287, \"text\": \"Poland\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Poland_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Poland_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The latest race content, interviews, features, reviews and expert buying guides, direct to your inbox!\", \"from\": 199, \"to\": 301, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You are now subscribed  Your newsletter sign-up was successful  Reigning Olympic and World ChampionJennifer Valenteof the United States secured the gold medal in the final cycling event of theParis Olympic Gameson Sunday.\", \"from\": 303, \"to\": 524, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Just four days earlier, Valente had also claimed gold in the women's team pursuit.\", \"from\": 525, \"to\": 607, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The American showcased her dominance in the first three events of the women's omnium, winning the scratch race and elimination race, and securing second place in the tempo race.\", \"from\": 609, \"to\": 786, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 613, \"end\": 621, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9999960757813514, \"rank\": 2.4514579273761463e-06, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Heading into the decisive points race, she had amassed 118 points, 10 more than Australia's Georgia Baker and 22 points on Canada's Maggie Coles-Lyster.\", \"from\": 787, \"to\": 939, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 867, \"end\": 876, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_national_rugby_union_team\", \"score\": 0.5459391793733749, \"rank\": 0.5757653746471626, \"text\": \"Australia\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_national_rugby_union_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_national_rugby_union_team\"}, {\"begin\": 879, \"end\": 892, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Georgia_Baker\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Georgia Baker\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Georgia_Baker\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Georgia_Baker\"}, {\"begin\": 910, \"end\": 916, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada_men's_national_ice_hockey_team\", \"score\": 0.4294446389842706, \"rank\": 0.8356755026555168, \"text\": \"Canada\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada_men's_national_ice_hockey_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada_men's_national_ice_hockey_team\"}, {\"begin\": 919, \"end\": 938, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Maggie_Coles-Lyster\", \"score\": 0.9999985358000946, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Maggie Coles-Lyster\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Maggie_Coles-Lyster\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Maggie_Coles-Lyster\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Bold attacks shook up the standings, setting the stage for an intense battle for the podium in the fourth and final event, while Valente held onto her lead.\", \"from\": 941, \"to\": 1097, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The American star ultimately clinched victory with 144 points.\", \"from\": 1098, \"to\": 1160, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1102, \"end\": 1115, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Standardbred\", \"score\": 0.9999691815093297, \"rank\": 3.0819440643225966e-05, \"text\": \"American star\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Standardbred\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Standardbred\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Poland's Daria Pikulik earned the silver medal with 131 points, and New Zealand'sAlly Wollastonsecured the bronze with 125 points.\", \"from\": 1161, \"to\": 1291, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1161, \"end\": 1167, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Poland_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9969016706212502, \"rank\": 0.002971336519427287, \"text\": \"Poland\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Poland_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Poland_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 1170, \"end\": 1183, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daria_Pikulik\", \"score\": 0.9999998782295808, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Daria Pikulik\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daria_Pikulik\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daria_Pikulik\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I went into the day to ride each of the four events as a standalone basically, and I think I did that pretty well and it worked out.\", \"from\": 1293, \"to\": 1426, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I definitely went into the points race looking at the couple of riders that were trailing me, and the points gap dropped a little bit once you get further down the startlist.\", \"from\": 1427, \"to\": 1601, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I was pretty happy to let other people take points and let the race evolve,\\\" Valente said.\", \"from\": 1602, \"to\": 1692, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's fantastic [to have won two gold medals].\", \"from\": 1694, \"to\": 1740, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"This has been a very long week, with the team pursuit qualifying a week ago, and I am really excited to pull it off on the last day.\\\"\", \"from\": 1741, \"to\": 1874, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Pikulik faced an officiating error during the elimination race when she was mistakenly eliminated by the race commissaires.\", \"from\": 1876, \"to\": 1999, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The mistake was corrected, and the race was yellow-flagged to allow her to rejoin the pack.\", \"from\": 2000, \"to\": 2091, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"She was ultimately eliminated in 10th place.\", \"from\": 2092, \"to\": 2136, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I can not describe in words how proud I am of myself today.\", \"from\": 2138, \"to\": 2198, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I did not start the Omnium in the way that I hoped for, and also in the elimination race, I do not know what happened.\", \"from\": 2199, \"to\": 2317, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It was like 'mistake Pikulik is out' and I was like, how is this possible?\\\"\", \"from\": 2318, \"to\": 2393, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"the Polish rider said.\", \"from\": 2394, \"to\": 2416, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2398, \"end\": 2404, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Poland\", \"score\": 0.9738428278218133, \"rank\": 0.02375792350609414, \"text\": \"Polish\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Poland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Poland\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The latest race content, interviews, features, reviews and expert buying guides, direct to your inbox!\", \"from\": 2418, \"to\": 2520, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I was not happy about it but, I also feel a little bit angry.\", \"from\": 2522, \"to\": 2584, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And after that, I just told myself you just go full gas from the start, no matter if you will be OK for the finish and that will be enough energy.\", \"from\": 2585, \"to\": 2731, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You just need to go full gas to be proud of yourself that you did it on your own and I did it.\\\"\", \"from\": 2732, \"to\": 2827, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Wollaston also won the silver in the team pursuit at Paris 2024.\", \"from\": 2829, \"to\": 2893, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2829, \"end\": 2838, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_Hyde_Wollaston\", \"score\": 0.9446440135118545, \"rank\": 0.05859817102144661, \"text\": \"Wollaston\", \"types\": [\"Q901\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_Hyde_Wollaston\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_Hyde_Wollaston\"}, {\"begin\": 2882, \"end\": 2892, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.56956541994907e-14, \"text\": \"Paris 2024\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I actually did not even know that I was in the bronze medal competition until maybe 10 laps to go.\", \"from\": 2895, \"to\": 2994, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And I heard my name, and I looked up on the board.\", \"from\": 2995, \"to\": 3045, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It was the first time I looked up and thought, 'Oh my god, yeah',\\\" Wollaston said.\", \"from\": 3046, \"to\": 3128, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3113, \"end\": 3122, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_Hyde_Wollaston\", \"score\": 0.9446440135118545, \"rank\": 0.05859817102144661, \"text\": \"Wollaston\", \"types\": [\"Q901\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_Hyde_Wollaston\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_Hyde_Wollaston\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Peter Stuart was editor of Cyclingnews from 2022 until 2025.\", \"from\": 3130, \"to\": 3190, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3130, \"end\": 3142, 